 to get the feel for blitzing them, they all have a slightly different set up but are also all very similar at the same time. the best missions for blitzing are non cave type missions. So anything in a built up area like 20k, Lush resort, harry's or broken shores is good. Don't worry too much about what the loot is, just how much the mission is worth in pure creds. <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.anarchy-online.com/character/bio/d/1/name/viirruss">Viirruss</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
