you need a bit more treament still, you could try to get a Quartz rifle that adds +10 treatment (QL22 is the lowest that still adds +10), if you can equip it, this can be tricky for MA's, but a wrangle or possibly a cheap rifle/aimed shot implant should do it. There are also things called treatment libraries that you can use to add a few points and tutoring devices for treatment can also give you just a touch more. Now all you need is to get some AGI, sense or STR/STA buffs. In case you are not familiar with them AGI is called feline grace, Sense is called Enhanced senses, and STR/STA buffs can be either Iron circle(+20 str/sta from a doc) or Essence from an enforcer (essence vary in how much they add by level of the nano, but they will stack with IC) i should also add that I don't think muscle stim (MA STR buff) will stack with either IC or essence.<br>
